1090
00:42:38,067 --> 00:42:39,467
We will die...

1091
00:42:39,467 --> 00:42:41,667
you will live.

1092
00:42:41,667 --> 00:42:43,801
Will you come to my funeral, John?

1093
00:42:43,801 --> 00:42:45,100
Hey, will...

1094
00:42:45,100 --> 00:42:46,334
you've gone too far.

1095
00:42:46,334 --> 00:42:48,501
John didn't ask to be what he is.

1096
00:42:48,501 --> 00:42:51,667
And we did not ask to hear about it.

1097
00:42:51,667 --> 00:42:53,234
But if it were true,

1098
00:42:53,234 --> 00:42:56,300
Is there one among us
who would not feel envy,

1099
00:42:56,300 --> 00:42:58,801
Even perhaps a touch of hatred?

1100
00:43:00,567 --> 00:43:02,234
You told us of yourself, John.

1101
00:43:02,234 --> 00:43:04,467
Can you imagine how we feel?

1102
00:43:04,467 --> 00:43:06,067
I never thought of that.

1103
00:43:06,067 --> 00:43:08,667
Since you may not die,

1104
00:43:08,667 --> 00:43:11,467
