1105
00:43:11,467 --> 00:43:13,634
there must be a reason for that, no?

1106
00:43:13,634 --> 00:43:15,501
Perhaps you are an expert.

1107
00:43:16,901 --> 00:43:19,434
Uh, that's it, Mr.
Oldman. Have a good one.

