1122
00:43:57,601 --> 00:44:00,067
But I sure as hell don't
like what you're doing.

1123
00:44:00,067 --> 00:44:02,501
Give me that gun or I'm
gonna break your goddamn arm.

1124
00:44:02,501 --> 00:44:05,834
You sound like our football coach, Dan.

1125
00:44:05,834 --> 00:44:07,801
What do you think, John?

1126
00:44:07,801 --> 00:44:09,801
A shot to the arm?

1127
00:44:09,801 --> 00:44:12,701
Perhaps we could watch it heal.

1128
00:44:12,701 --> 00:44:15,501
A bullet in
the head--

1129
00:44:15,501 --> 00:44:17,033
What exactly will happen?

1130
00:44:23,000 --> 00:44:25,200
I have papers to correct.

1131
00:44:25,200 --> 00:44:28,100
As much as I dislike that job,

1132
00:44:28,100 --> 00:44:30,634
It'll be preferable to this.

